<kml>
<property-doc name=Blue-Reserve-Availability>
<system-documentation name=Blue-Reserve-Availability>
<gpd-documentation name=CritiqueScores>

<description>
Doctrinally, commanders are required to designate a reserve force.  In the field, a force may not be available as a dedicated reserve.  Often a unit will be given a mission assignment and told to be prepared to act as a reserve force in an emergency.
</description>

<example>
Is there a sufficient force to assign a reserve mission?<br><br>
Has a reserve mission been assigned to a particular unit?<br><br>
Is the designated reserve unit adequate for probable contingencies?<br><br>
</example>

</kml>
